cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image stylization using deep learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of adversarial training, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves generating mosaics, which can be considered as a graphics-related task (cs.GR) and involves manipulating images (cs.MM).
